OL,3,CAsylum seeker boat pilot loses bid to
OL,4,Cchallenge convictions and sentence
OL,6,FAn asylum seeker convicted of
OL,7,Fmanslaughter after four migrants died
OL,8,Fas he steered a boat across the
OL,9,FEnglish Channel has lost his bid to
OL,10,Fchallenge his convictions and sentence.
OL,12,FIbrahima Bah was sentenced to nine and
OL,13,Fa half years' detention after the
OL,14,Fdeaths as he piloted the "unseaworthy"
OL,15,Fboat between France and the UK on 14
OL,16,FDecember 2022.
