OL,3,CAsylum seeker boat pilot loses bid to
OL,4,Cchallenge convictions and sentence
OL,6,FDuring a retrial at Canterbury Crown
OL,7,FCourt, Bah said smugglers threatened
OL,8,Fto kill him if he did not drive the
OL,9,Fboat, but the prosecution said he was
OL,10,Fnot telling the truth and he owed his
OL,11,Ffellow passengers a "duty of care" as
OL,12,Ftheir pilot.
OL,14,FThe Senegalese national was also
OL,15,Fconvicted of facilitating illegal
OL,16,Fentry to the UK.
OL,18,FAt a hearing earlier this month, Bah
OL,19,Fbrought his case to the Court of
OL,20,FAppeal in a bid for the green light to
OL,21,Fchallenge his convictions and sentence.
