OL,3,CAsylum seeker boat pilot loses bid to
OL,4,Cchallenge convictions and sentence
OL,6,FIn a ruling on Wednesday, the Lady
OL,7,FChief Justice Baroness Carr said Bah
OL,8,Fcould not bring the appeal, ruling it
OL,9,Fwas not "arguable".
OL,11,FRichard Thomas KC, for Bah, previously
OL,12,Fdescribed his trial as "touching on a
OL,13,Fhighly politicised issue which gives
OL,14,Frise to very strong feelings".
OL,16,FJurors heard that the home-built, low-
OL,17,Fquality inflatable should have had no
OL,18,Fmore than 20 people on board but
OL,19,Fcarried about 45 people in the English
OL,20,FChannel that night.
