OL,6,FThe barrister continued: "It was not
OL,7,Fthe background or the scene setting...
OL,8,Fit was the continued act of
OL,9,Ffacilitation at the time of their
OL,10,Fdeaths which provided the
OL,11,Fcircumstances in which the deaths
OL,12,Foccurred."
OL,14,FA total of 39 survivors were brought
OL,15,Fto shore in the port of Dover after a
OL,16,FUK fishing boat crew came across the
OL,17,Fsinking dinghy with help from the
OL,18,FRNLI, air ambulance and UK Border
OL,19,FForce.
